OL,3,CCheaper food and free bus rides:
OL,4,CWhat's in Reeves' cost of living plan?
OL,6,FFree summer bus rides for children and
OL,7,Fpossible reductions on some food
OL,8,Ftariffs are part of a raft of measures
OL,9,Fbeing set out by Chancellor Rachel
OL,10,FReeves to ease the impact of the Iran
OL,11,Fwar.
OL,13,FWith the conflict in the Middle East
OL,14,Fdriving up global oil prices and
OL,15,Fdisrupting the commercial shipping of
OL,16,Feveryday goods, British consumers have
OL,17,Fbeen feeling the pinch beyond petrol
OL,18,Fstation forecourts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
