OL,3,CCheaper food and free bus rides:
OL,4,CWhat's in Reeves' cost of living plan?
OL,6,FIn the Commons on Thursday, Reeves is
OL,7,Fset to give details of policies to
OL,8,Ftackle the cost-of-living squeeze
OL,9,Ftriggered by Donald Trump's war on
OL,10,FIran.
OL,12,FThe government is cutting import
OL,13,Ftariffs on more than 100 types of
OL,14,Fproducts in a move that is expected to
OL,15,Fsave consumers more than #150 million
OL,16,Fa year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
