OL,3,CCheaper food and free bus rides:
OL,4,CWhat's in Reeves' cost of living plan?
OL,6,FThe chancellor has also set out a
OL,7,F"Great British Summer Savings" scheme,
OL,8,Fincluding free bus travel for children
OL,9,Fin England during the school holidays
OL,10,Fin August.
OL,12,FThe household energy price cap is
OL,13,Fpredicted to rise by #209 a year from
OL,14,FJuly after the closure of the Strait
OL,15,Fof Hormuz pushed up global oil and gas
OL,16,Fprices ` but Reeves is not expected to
OL,17,Fannounce immediate help with rising
OL,18,Fenergy bills.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
