OL,3,CCheaper food and free bus rides:
OL,4,CWhat's in Reeves' cost of living plan?
OL,6,FReeves may set out more details of her
OL,7,Fcontingency planning, but she is
OL,8,Fexpected to wait until September
OL,9,Fbefore finalising any package of
OL,10,Ftargeted support for households over
OL,11,Fthe winter months, when more energy is
OL,12,Fused.
OL,14,FEasing prices on food
OL,16,FThe plan to suspend tariffs on some
OL,17,Ffood imports is part of the
OL,18,Fgovernment's wider effort to combat
OL,19,Frising prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
