OL,3,CCheaper food and free bus rides:
OL,4,CWhat's in Reeves' cost of living plan?
OL,6,FThe full list of products will be
OL,7,Fpublished next week, but is expected
OL,8,Fto include biscuits, chocolate, dried
OL,9,Ffruit and nuts.
OL,11,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said:
OL,12,F"We know many hardworking families
OL,13,Fare still feeling the squeeze and too
OL,14,Foften think they have to hold back.
OL,16,F"By giving every child free bus travel
OL,17,Fthroughout August and cutting tariffs
OL,18,Fon everyday food items, we're putting
OL,19,Fmoney back into people's pockets and
OL,20,Fmaking life that bit easier.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
