OL,3,CCheaper food and free bus rides:
OL,4,CWhat's in Reeves' cost of living plan?
OL,6,FThe chancellor is committing more than
OL,7,F#100 million to fund the free fares
OL,8,Fscheme and to support bus services
OL,9,Ffacing increased costs.
OL,11,FReeves said: "My number one priority
OL,12,Fis protecting households from rising
OL,13,Fcosts.
OL,15,F"This summer I want every family to be
OL,16,Fable to enjoy themselves, that's why
OL,17,Fwe're launching the Great British
OL,18,FSummer Savings Scheme, and why we're
OL,19,Fhelping kids with free bus travel
OL,20,Fthroughout August.
OL,26,@sD@NOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
