OL,3,CCheaper food and free bus rides:
OL,4,CWhat's in Reeves' cost of living plan?
OL,6,F"As the war in Iran pushes prices up
OL,7,Fat home, my economic plan is the right
OL,8,Fone. I will continue to make the right
OL,9,Fchoices, to protect households and
OL,10,Fbusinesses, and build a stronger and
OL,11,Fmore secure Britain."
OL,13,FInflation dipped in April ` but is
OL,14,Fexpected to surge back up
OL,16,FThe latest package comes after the
OL,17,FGovernment announced an extension of
OL,18,Fthe 5p cut in fuel duty until the end
OL,19,Fof the year, along with a tax break
OL,20,Ffor hauliers and help with red diesel
OL,21,Fcosts for farmers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
