OL,3,CCheaper food and free bus rides:
OL,4,CWhat's in Reeves' cost of living plan?
OL,6,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,7,F(ONS) said Consumer Prices Index (CPI)
OL,8,Finflation fell to 2.8% in April, down
OL,9,Ffrom 3.3% in March, and the lowest
OL,10,Flevel since March 2025.
OL,12,FBut this was largely driven by
OL,13,Fregulator Ofgem lowering the energy
OL,14,Fprice cap from the start of April by
OL,15,F7%, or #10 a month, for the average
OL,16,Fhousehold using both electricity and
OL,17,Fgas, which was pushed down by
OL,18,FGovernment measures to reduce bills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
