OL,3,CCheaper food and free bus rides:
OL,4,CWhat's in Reeves' cost of living plan?
OL,6,FInflation is expected to surge back up
OL,7,Fas the conflict in the Middle East has
OL,8,Fsent fuel prices soaring, and the
OL,9,Fenergy price cap is expected to
OL,10,Fincrease significantly from July when
OL,11,Fit is next updated.
OL,13,FEnergy analyst Cornwall Insight's
OL,14,Fprediction for Ofgem's cap from July
OL,15,Fto September now stands at #1,850 for
OL,16,Fa typical dual fuel household, an
OL,17,Fincrease of 13% on April's #1,641
OL,18,Fannual cap.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
