OL,3,CCheaper food and free bus rides:
OL,4,CWhat's in Reeves' cost of living plan?
OL,6,FMinisters are wary of a Liz Truss-
OL,7,Fstyle universal bailout for all
OL,8,Fhouseholds, warning that unfunded
OL,9,Fgiveaways could trigger an increase in
OL,10,Fgovernment borrowing costs and
OL,11,Finflation, feeding through to higher
OL,12,Fmortgage rates, which would end up
OL,13,Fleaving people worse off.
